commitTranslationEditorPopupInAppsTable

public static void commitTranslationEditorPopupInAppsTable(org.w3c.dom.Element applicationsTable,
                                                           org.w3c.dom.Element translationAfTable,
                                                           WrappedAccessorDefinition translationAccessor,
                                                           org.w3c.dom.Element popup,
                                                           org.w3c.dom.Element commandToolbarButton,
                                                           org.w3c.dom.Document document,
                                                           oracle.adfdt.ADFDesignTimeContext dtContext,
                                                           java.lang.String dialogId)
Commit the translation editor popup. All sub-elements will be created if not currently present.

Parameters:
applicationsTable - table enclosing all this work. We will add to various places in this xml tree.
translationAfTable - table to add.
popup - if we are dropped as a popup this will be non-null and we decorate it as the popup content, the button will be added to under applicationsTable.
commandToolbarButton - as a commandToolbarButton this will be non-null and we decorate it as the button content, the popup will be added to under applicationsTable.
document - the document.
dtContext - the context.
dialogId - the id of the dialog.
